{"data":[{"name":"70:1","price":"有人曾请求一种将发生的刑罚。","arabic":"سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5376,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:2","price":"那是为不信的人们而预定的，没有任何人能加以抵抗。","arabic":"لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5377,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:3","price":"那是安拉--天梯的主宰--发出的，","arabic":"مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5378,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:4","price":"众天使和精神在一日之内升到他那里。那一日的长度是五万年。","arabic":"تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5379,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:5","price":"你安然地忍受吧。","arabic":"فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5380,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:6","price":"他们以为那刑罚是很远的，","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5381,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:7","price":"我却以为那是很近的。","arabic":"وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5382,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:8","price":"在那日天像熔铜，","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَكُونُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ كَٱلۡمُهۡلِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5383,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:9","price":"山像彩绒。","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5384,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:10","price":"亲戚相见不相问。","arabic":"وَلَا يَسۡـَٔلُ حَمِيمٌ حَمِيمٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5385,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:11","price":"罪人愿意赎取那日的刑罚，即使牺牲他的儿女、","arabic":"يُبَصَّرُونَهُمۡۚ يَوَدُّ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُ لَوۡ يَفۡتَدِي مِنۡ عَذَابِ يَوۡمِئِذِۭ بِبَنِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5386,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:12","price":"他的妻子、他的弟兄，","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5387,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:13","price":"和那收容他的血族，","arabic":"وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5388,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:14","price":"以及大地上所有的人，但愿那能拯救自己。","arabic":"وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5389,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:15","price":"绝不然，那确是发焰的烈火，","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهَا لَظَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5390,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:16","price":"能揭去头皮，","arabic":"نَزَّاعَةٗ لِّلشَّوَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5391,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:17","price":"能召唤转身而逃避的人。","arabic":"تَدۡعُواْ مَنۡ أَدۡبَرَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5392,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:18","price":"他曾聚集财产加以保藏，","arabic":"وَجَمَعَ فَأَوۡعَىٰٓ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5393,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:19","price":"人确是被造成浮躁的，","arabic":"۞ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5394,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:20","price":"遭遇灾殃的时候是烦恼的，","arabic":"إِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ جَزُوعٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5395,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:21","price":"获得财富的时候是吝啬的。","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلۡخَيۡرُ مَنُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5396,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:22","price":"只有礼拜的人们，不是那样，","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5397,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:23","price":"他们是常守拜功的；","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ دَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5398,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:24","price":"他们的财产中有一个定份，","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ فِيٓ أَمۡوَٰلِهِمۡ حَقّٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5399,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:25","price":"是用于施济乞丐和贫民的；","arabic":"لِّلسَّآئِلِ وَٱلۡمَحۡرُومِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5400,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:26","price":"他们是承认报应之日的；","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ يُصَدِّقُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5401,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:27","price":"他们是畏惧他们的主的刑罚的。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم مِّنۡ عَذَابِ رَبِّهِم مُّشۡفِقُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5402,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:28","price":"他们的主的刑罚，确是难保不降临的。","arabic":"إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّهِمۡ غَيۡرُ مَأۡمُونٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5403,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:29","price":"他们是保守贞操的，","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِفُرُوجِهِمۡ حَٰفِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5404,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:30","price":"除非他们对自己的妻子和奴婢，他们确是不因此而受责备的；","arabic":"إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5405,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:31","price":"凡在这个范围之外有所要求的人，都是过份的。","arabic":"فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5406,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:32","price":"他们是尊重自己所受的信托，和自己所缔的盟约的；","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5407,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:33","price":"他们是秉公作证的；","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5408,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:34","price":"他们是谨守拜功的。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5409,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:35","price":"这等人，是在乐园中受优待的。","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5410,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:36","price":"不信道的人们，怎么注视着你们，三五成群的分列","arabic":"فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5411,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:37","price":"在你的左右呢？","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5412,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:38","price":"难道他们每个人都希望入恩泽的乐园吗？","arabic":"أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5413,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:39","price":"绝不然！我确已用他们所知道的物质创造了他们。","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5414,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:40","price":"不然，我以一切东方和西方的主盟誓，我确是全能的，","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡمَشَٰرِقِ وَٱلۡمَغَٰرِبِ إِنَّا لَقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5415,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:41","price":"我能以比他们更好的人代替他们，我不是无能的。","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ خَيۡرٗا مِّنۡهُمۡ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5416,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:42","price":"你应当任他们妄谈，任他们游戏，直到他们看到他们所被警告的日子。","arabic":"فَذَرۡهُمۡ يَخُوضُواْ وَيَلۡعَبُواْ حَتَّىٰ يُلَٰقُواْ يَوۡمَهُمُ ٱلَّذِي يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5417,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:43","price":"在那日，他们将从坟中出来奔走，他们好像奔到牌位一样，","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَخۡرُجُونَ مِنَ ٱلۡأَجۡدَاثِ سِرَاعٗا كَأَنَّهُمۡ إِلَىٰ نُصُبٖ يُوفِضُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5418,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"70:44","price":"同时，他们身遭凌辱，不敢仰视。那是他们被警告的日子。","arabic":"خَٰشِعَةً أَبۡصَٰرُهُمۡ تَرۡهَقُهُمۡ ذِلَّةٞۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلَّذِي كَانُواْ يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5419,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij","Chapter Al-Ma'arij","Ma'arij","Surah Ma'arij","Chapter Ma'arij","Al Ma'arij","Surah Al Ma'arij","Chapter Al Ma'arij","Surah 70","Chapter 70","The Ascending Stairways","المعارج"]}